headline: Is State Street Still a Smart Play After Its 27% 2024 Rally and New Partnerships?
summary: Wondering if State Street is a smart place to put your money right now? Let’s talk about what’s behind the numbers and whether this stock could still offer value. State Street shares have climbed impressively, up 27.1% over the past year and a massive 105.7% over five years, with a healthy 19.7% gain so far in 2024. These price moves make more sense when you look at the recent news spotlighting increased institutional activity and heightened interest from the financial sector in State...
